collections.name: EVO
collections.description:
Each piece in this collection represents a moment of metamorphosis - capturing real human movements, skills, and expressions, then enhancing them through advanced 3D modeling and AI-generated imagery. The artist, both subject and creator, documents their own transformation from flesh to circuitry, from limitation to possibility.
"EVO" challenges our perception of what it means to be human in an increasingly technological world. Through skateboarding, urban environments, and futuristic aesthetics, these NFTs tell the story of our collective journey toward a post-human existence where the limits of truth dissolve.
Created using open-source tools like ComfyUI, this collection stands as both art and manifesto - a declaration that we can preserve our human essence while transcending our limitations. Each NFT captures a fragment of this evolution, frozen in time yet pulsing with kinetic energy.

#CyberEvolution #PostHuman #AIArt #DigitalTransformation #NFTCollection

A journey into melting forms, blinking voids, and stories only the inner mind dares to tell.

collections.name: KOBE
collections.description:
KOBE – A Port City Reimagined Through Art
Nestled between mountains and sea, Kobe is a city where tradition meets modernity, and international culture blends with Japanese soul.
This collection captures the spirit of Kobe — not just its skyline or famous landmarks, but its atmosphere, rhythm, and resilience.

KOBE is a visual tribute to the city's charm: the iconic Port Tower, the ships sailing into its harbor, and the timeless Kobe Tartan pattern, all reimagined through digital art.

Every piece in this collection is a window into Kobe’s identity — minimalist yet emotional, modern yet nostalgic. Whether you've walked its streets or are discovering it for the first time, these works invite you to experience Kobe in a new way.

Art from Japan's port city, to the world.
